@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Sydney's Strung Creations";
}

<div class="container">
    <div class="about-header">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Sydney Strung Creations Jewelry Store, where beauty meets elegance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-image-text">
            <figure class="about-figure">
                <img src="~/images/founder.jpg" alt="Sydney" class="about-image">
                <figcaption class="image-caption">Sydney, the creative mind behind Strung Creations and her sister, Savannah, in the woods.</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>Founded in 2024, Sydney started making jewelry in high school using modified kandi patterns. From there, she found a passion for creating pieces she couldn’t find elsewhere. At first, she made things for herself, then for her sister and friends. After much pestering, she decided to create a shop. Inspired by color schemes, characters, or concepts, she aims to create jewelry that sparks the same joy in others that the creation does in herself.</p>

                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is to provide customers with beautiful, high-quality jewelry that can be treasured for a lifetime. We strive to offer impeccable customer service, with fast shipping and easy returns, to ensure a satisfying shopping experience.</p>

                <h2>Our Values</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Customer Satisfaction: We prioritize your happiness with each purchase.</li>
                    <li>Craftsmanship: Every piece is handmade with great care and precision.</li>
                    <li>Integrity: We believe in ethical business practices and fair pricing.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions or would like to learn more about our products, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:sydneystrungcreations@outlook.com">sydneystrungcreations@outlook.com</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .about-image-text {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .about-figure {
        width: 40%;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .about-image {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .image-caption {
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #555;
        margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .about-text {
        width: 55%;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
</style>
